msgctxt "5||rizap||table||83||||2"
msgid "Hi there, Kiryu-san! This time, let's go for a\r\ndish low in sugar and high in protein. Oh,\r\nyeah... I suggest a nutritious dish that's\r\npacked with lobster! Well then, best of luck!"
