msgctxt "5||rizap||table||84||||2"
msgid "Hi there, Kiryu-san! This time, let's go for a\r\nbulk-up meal. Let's see... I suggest a dish\r\nwhere you can consume rice, pork, and egg\r\nall together! Well then, best of luck!"
