msgctxt "10||cabaret_sora||table||11||||2"
msgid "Huh? Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||sub_a26_00||table||1||||2"
msgid "Kiryu-san!\r\nIt's Sodachi. I've finally gotten strong enough\r\nto earn the title of the strongest. I'll be waiting\r\nat the Children's Park. You haven't even seen\r\nmy final form!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||sub_b26_00||table||1||||2"
msgid "I've finally figured out the ultimate self-defense\r\ntechnique. However, it's not complete yet. I\r\nneed to defeat you with it to truly complete it,\r\nKiryu-san. Please accept this challenge. I'll be\r\nwaiting at the Ropeway Station."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||sub_b19_gen||table||1||||2"
msgid "Smartphones are so useful! I'm at New Gaudi\r\nright now. You should come on over, too,\r\nKiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||1||||2"
msgid "Hey, are you free?\r\nI could use a hand with something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||2||||2"
msgid "Can you head over to a convenience store\r\nand buy me some prepaid cards?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||3||||2"
msgid "Don't worry what they are.\r\nJust get them for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||4||||2"
msgid "Good. Buy five \\10,000 cards."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||5||||2"
msgid "Tell me when you have them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||6||||2"
msgid "Good. Now send me photos of the numbers on\r\neach one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||7||||2"
msgid "Family issues."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||8||||2"
msgid "Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||9||||2"
msgid "Just send them already.\r\nI'm in a hurry here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||10||||2"
msgid "Fine. Let's meet up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||11||||2"
msgid "The roof of the Senryo Building."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||12||||2"
msgid "What the hell's going on, Kiryu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||13||||2"
msgid "Kiryu, you've been had!\r\nMy account got hacked the other day!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||14||||2"
msgid "That wasn't me you were talking to!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||15||||2"
msgid "Your 50 grand could be anywhere by now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||16||||2"
msgid "No, dammit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||17||||2"
msgid "I'll see what I can do.\r\nThat scammer's not getting away with this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||18||||2"
msgid "Sorry, 50 grand's a lot to lose.\r\nI'll buy you a drink sometime to make up for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||19||||2"
msgid "Kiryu, I just found out my account got hacked!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||20||||2"
msgid "You \"handled\" it? How?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||21||||2"
msgid "You ran into some criminals? Where?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||22||||2"
msgid "I'll send some guys to clean this up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||sub_a12_00||table||23||||2"
msgid "Spare me the details, but it sounds like I owe \r\nyou a drink."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||sub_a99_00||table||1||||2"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu, my eternal rival.\r\nThe time has come yet again.\r\n\r\nI await you on my floating island.\r\n-Jo Amon"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||2||||2"
msgid "Nice to meet you! My name's Hiro. I distribute\r\nthe Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nThis newsletter will tell you everything you\r\nneed to know to get the most out of your\r\ngame. \r\n\r\nIf there's something you don't understand, I\r\nhope you'll look to us for help!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||3||||2"
msgid "Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||4||||2"
msgid "Huh? Are you angry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||5||||2"
msgid "Haha, thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||6||||2"
msgid "I'm sorry to surprise you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||7||||2"
msgid "I'm glad you're happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||8||||2"
msgid "What!? Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||9||||2"
msgid "What's the matter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||10||||2"
msgid "I'm excited to talk to you, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||11||||2"
msgid "Do you still not understand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||12||||2"
msgid "Hahaha! That's impossible. Although, I'd\r\nlove to grab a drink with you if I could."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||13||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nToday we'll talk about saving. This game has \r\nan auto-save function, so you don't need to\r\nfind phone booths. It's 2016, right? Keep in\r\nmind, when the save mark is being displayed,\r\ndon't turn off the system as it could corrupt\r\nyour data.\r\n\r\nIf you'd rather manually save the game, select\r\n\"Settings\" from your phone and you'll find the\r\noption there. You can't manually save during\r\nevents or battles. \r\n\r\nYour save data acts as a bookmark so you can\r\npick up the game from wherever you left off.\r\nContinue a saved game by selecting \"Continue\"\r\nfrom the Title Screen.\r\n"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||14||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\n\nThis newsletter is all about the map. The mini\nmap is displayed in the lower-left corner,\nshowing your surroundings, points of interest,\nand enemies. Just press <Action=View_Map,Adventure> \nto display the entire map, which you can create\nwaypoint markers on! Use both maps to figure\nout where you're headed and how to get there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||15||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\n\nWhile wandering out in the world, you can\nsprint by holding down <Sign:9,Adventure>.\nCompared to your normal speed, you'll run \na lot faster. However, if you run for too long,\nyou'll become winded.\nLet go of <Sign:9,Adventure> and catch your breath\nwhen needed. Pacing yourself is important! If\nyou want to sprint for longer stretches, there\nare upgrades for that in the Stats Menu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||16||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nWhen you press <Sign:8,Adventure> while you have control of\r\nKiryu, you'll shift to a first-person perspective.\r\nIt can feel very immersive to see the world\r\nthrough Kiryu's eyes. You may even find secrets\r\nwhile in the first-person point of view that\r\nyou wouldn't have seen otherwise. However, if\r\nyou get in a fight or start a conversation, you'll\r\nswitch back to third-person view."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||17||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nI want to tell you about an app called \"Awards\"\r\non your smartphone. You'll earn some valuable\r\nEXP for objectives you complete here. Clearing\r\nsome easy objectives is a good way to get EXP\r\nearly on. New objectives become available as\r\nyou clear previous ones, so keep at them as\r\nmuch as you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||18||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nThere are some great local restaurants to check\r\nout when you just want to relax, recover lost\r\nhealth, and gain a bit of EXP. Certain meal\r\ncombinations may even give you bonus EXP. \r\n\r\nBut don't go too crazy! Eating after you're\r\nalready full will recover health, but not grant\r\nEXP. How do you get hungry again? By burning\r\ncalories, silly! Whether it's running around the\r\ncity or beating up street trash, you're sure to\r\nwork up an appetite doing what you do best!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||19||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nDid you know you can change the time of day\r\nby accessing either the waiting room door of\r\nNew Serena in Kamurocho, or the futon at the\r\nNavy Apartments when you're in Onomichi?\r\nKeep in mind, you won't be able to change the\r\ntime of day at certain points in the story. You\r\ncan choose either Day or Night in Kamurocho,\r\nand Day, Dusk, or Night in Onomichi. Certain\r\nevents only happen during specific times, so be\r\nsure to explore at all different times."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||20||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nJust like real life, if you consume too much\r\nalcohol, you'll get drunk. You can sober up\r\nby drinking water or even just letting it wear\r\noff as time passes. When you're drunk, people\r\naround the city are more likely to pick a fight\r\nwith you. At the same time, your Heat Orbs\r\nwill fill faster, so sometimes you may want to\r\nget drunk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||21||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nAs you advance through the story, you'll find\r\nitems that are considered Valuables. Valuables\r\nhave their own tab in the Items Menu where\r\nyou can read descriptions of each one.\r\nValuables are often items that are important\r\nto the story. You cannot throw away or sell\r\nValuables."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||tips_system||table||22||||2"
msgid "This is Hiro from the Tips Newsletter!\r\n\r\nWhen you obtain DLC, a cardboard box will be\r\ndelivered to either New Serena in Kamurocho\r\nor the Navy Apartments in Onomichi. Check\r\nthe box to unlock your DLC. You can only\r\nunlock DLC once per save file."
msgstr ""

