msgid "Do you want to become stronger? Sure, we all\r\ndo. So, read my emails to find out just how\r\neasy it is. First we have to get you used to\r\nperforming simple attacks. \r\n\r\n<Sign:2,Combat><Sign:1,Combat><Sign:1,Combat>\r\n<Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:1,Combat><Sign:1,Combat>\r\n<Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:1,Combat><Sign:1,Combat>\r\n<Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:2,Combat><Sign:1,Combat><Sign:1,Combat>\r\n\r\n - Battle Master"
msgstr ""

