msgctxt "18||tips_btlmaster||table||13||||2"
msgid "It looks like you're pretty out of shape. So, I'll\r\nneed to teach you the basics again. Sure,\r\nattacking is important in a fight, but defense\r\ncan be even more crucial. Practice using all\r\nof the following defenses: \r\n\r\nHold <Sign:4,Combat> while moving to strafe around an\r\nenemy.\r\n\r\nHold <Sign:6,Combat> to guard against enemy attacks.\r\n\r\nPress <Sign: 3,Combat> to Quickstep.\r\n\r\nIf you can do those, just wait for an opening\r\nand then unleash your attacks.\r\n\r\n - Battle Master"
