msgctxt "18||tips_btlmaster||table||46||||2"
msgid "So you're probably getting used to battles by\r\nnow. That's great! But, don't you hate being\r\nsurrounded by enemies and assaulted from all\r\nsides? Don't worry! In those situations, grab an\r\nenemy with <Sign:0,Combat>, then press <Sign:0,Combat> again to throw\r\nthem. You can do this to knock down\r\nsurrounding enemies as well.  \r\n\r\nHave you ever had a difficult time with speedy\r\nenemies? For quick foes, grab them using <Sign:0,Combat>,\r\nthen perform a grab attack by pressing <Sign:2,Combat> or\r\n<Sign:1,Combat>. Stopping an enemy's movement is the most\r\nsurefire way to cause damage.\r\n\r\nYou can also pick up weapons lying around\r\ntown with <Sign:0,Combat>. Weapons like knives and firearms\r\ncan't be guarded against, so use them whenever\r\nyou can. You have to be prepared to defend\r\nyourself against people who don't fight fair.\r\n\r\n - Battle Master"
msgstr ""

