msgctxt "18||tips_btlmaster||table||79||||2"
msgid "Long time no see. I've watched you for a while,\r\nand it seems your fighting skills are pretty top\r\nnotch now. Therefore, this will be my final\r\nadvice to you.\r\n\r\nAs the Dragon of Dojima, you must understand\r\nthat training can only take you so far. If you\r\nhaven't yet, master your Basic Stats to the max.\r\nOnly then can you push beyond your limits.\r\n\r\nI'll contact you again... when the time is right.\r\n\r\nUntil then, keep on training.\r\n\r\n - Battle Master"
msgstr ""

