msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||1||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nI knew you could do it, Kiryu-san! Looks like\r\nyou drove the shakedown army out of the\r\ncity. They don't want to mess with you again.\r\nYou've brought this town one step closer to\r\npeace. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||12||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nWow! What an incredible job, Kiryu-san!\r\nThose guys were seeking out middle-aged\r\nmen to assault, but you sent them packing!\r\nPlease continue to help however you can!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||23||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThose pick-up artists were going around\r\ntricking a lot of girls. Thankfully, they\r\nshouldn't con anyone else now that you've\r\ntaught them some manners. You're really\r\nturning this town around for the better.\r\nThank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||34||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nIt turns out those guys had committed a lot\r\nof assaults as a mob in this city. \r\n\r\nYou inspired some courage in people who\r\nsaw you fight without any fear against guys\r\nlike that, Kiryu-san. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||45||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThose guys were notorious as monsters who\r\ntarget couples. What do you think warped their\r\nhearts? Oh well. We don't have to worry about\r\nthem. They won't show their faces around here\r\nanymore. Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||56||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nI'm sorry, but I had to laugh. I never thought I\r\nwould see you deliver ramen. It might have\r\nbeen a pain in the ass, but I'm sure you saved\r\nthat restaurant... lol. You're doing great work!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||67||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThat settles the series of arsons that had been\r\nhappening in Kamurocho. If it weren't for you,\r\nthere could have been a serious disaster in this\r\ncity. You really saved us all. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||78||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThat settles the series of arsons that had\r\nbeen happening in Onomichi. If it weren't\r\nfor Troublr, we might not have been able\r\nto stop it. I'm thinking of taking this system\r\nnationwide. Let's work together to keep the\r\npeace in this city. I can't thank you enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||89||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nI guess you could say you're in big trouble if\r\nyou run out of toilet paper... lol. I'm in awe of\r\nyour kindness! It's nice to solve small problems\r\nlike this once in a while for a change of pace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||100||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThat was a really dangerous criminal. I wish\r\nthe police would catch people like that and\r\nkeep them off the streets. You've done a\r\ngreat service to your fellow man, Kiryu-san.\r\nThank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||111||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThere's a correlation between the crime rate\r\nin a city and the amount of purse-snatchers.\r\nWithout any witnesses, victims generally have\r\nno option but to give up. You were able to\r\ncatch them in the act of the crime, though.\r\nThank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||122||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nI think this city is still very dangerous. The\r\nguy who was caught was apparently an infamous\r\npickpocket according to the police. Looks like\r\nhe was outclassed this time. LOL. Thank you,\r\nKiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||133||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nYou really saved us. He might have been the\r\nmost terrifying threat so far. You can make\r\nbombs so easily nowadays... So we can't rule\r\nout the possibility that more bombers might\r\nappear later. I'll keep a look out. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||trouble_mail||table||144||||2"
msgid "This is Torafuru.\r\n\r\nThanks to you, this city has become much\r\nmore peaceful. I think as long as we keep an\r\neye on Troublr, we'll be able to manage. \r\n\r\nYou're an inspiration, Kiryu-san. I want to\r\nbecome strong like you. I want to protect\r\nthis city with my own strength, rather than\r\nalways depending on others.\r\n\r\nThat's how I feel now. I'll keep working at it.\r\nThank you for everything. Goodbye."
msgstr ""

