msgid "Kiryu-san,\r\n\r\nThat back-alley merchant that I talked to you\r\nabout the other day gave me a call. He said it\r\nwas okay for me to tell you about him, so if\r\nyou want to meet him, you should check out the\r\nvacant lot in Hana-no-kubo."
